9#include <isl_multi_macro.h>
10#include <isl/hash.h>
11
12/* Return a hash value that digests "multi".
13 */
14uint32_t FN(MULTI(BASE),get_hash)(__isl_keep MULTI(BASE) *multi)
15{
16 int i;
17 uint32_t hash;
18
19 if (!multi)
20 return 0;
21
22 hash = isl_hash_init();
23 for (i = 0; i < multi->n; ++i) {
24 uint32_t el_hash;
25 el_hash = FN(EL,get_hash)(multi->u.p[i]);
26 isl_hash_hash(hash, el_hash);
27 }
28
29 return hash;
30}
